com.gh.bmd.jrt.android.builder

Interface ObjectServiceRoutineBuilder

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ClassRoutineBuilder, ConfigurableBuilder, ObjectRoutineBuilder, ServiceRoutineBuilder, SharableBuilder

    public interface ObjectServiceRoutineBuilder
extends ServiceRoutineBuilder, ObjectRoutineBuilder
    Class implementing a builder of routine objects based on methods of a concrete object instance.

    The single methods can be accessed via reflection or the whole instance can be proxied through an interface.

    Created by davide on 3/29/15.

      • withArgs

        @Nonnull
ObjectServiceRoutineBuilder withArgs(@Nullable
                                           Object... args)
        Sets the arguments to be passed to the wrapped instance factory.

        Note that, like the object passed to the service routine input and output channels, the specified arguments must comply with the Parcel.writeValue(Object) method. Be aware though, that issues may arise when employing Serializable objects on the Lollipop OS version, so, it is advisable to use Parcelable objects instead.

        Parameters:
        args - the arguments.
        Returns:
        this builder.
